title: Izvoraș-67
text: Izvoraş-67 was a <a href="Moldova">Moldova</a>n <a href="football%20%28soccer%29">football</a> club based in <a href="Ratu%C8%99">Ratuș</a>, <a href="Moldova">Moldova</a>. They have played in the <a href="Moldovan%20%26quot%3BA%26quot%3B%20Division">Moldovan "A" Division</a>, the second division in Moldovan football in season 2008–09 and won Division B North.
